    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>As reported by Waldemar Schott on fw-general:</p>

<p>I think it would be nice if Zend_Mail supports fluent interfaces  like other parts of the framework.</p>

<p>$mail = new Zend_Mail();
$mail-&gt;setBodyText('This is the text of the mail.')
    -&gt;setFrom('somebody@example.com', 'Some Sender')
    -&gt;addTo('somebody_else@example.com', 'Some Recipient')
    -&gt;setSubject('TestSubject')
    -&gt;send();|</p>

